thread.title: Mariella

author: Mariella
title: Mariella
text:
very trustworthy and efficient, solving any issues immediately. In Australia we have quite restrictive process now to send money overseas by HiFX has helped me with any hurdles and got it all done. I send money to South America which can be difficult and have had no problems they couldn't resolve.
I have no reason to use anyone else, as it as an all encompassing service
